{
  "stem": "142.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were-- but the Italians had a lot of affairs at that time, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had dances.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we used to go there, because we were part of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We speak a couple of languages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we spoke Greek, Italian, and Ladino.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We speak mostly Greek and Ladino.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the two languages we-- we used to speak.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were speaking Greek, actually, with our friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- we had quite a few Gentile friends, you know, but mostly were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our friends were mostly Jewish, because at one point, when I was in the Italian school, I used to belong also to the-- to Jewish organizations, you know, the-- the Jabotinsky actually.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were always-- at that time, you know, Israel, you know, was Palestine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were always talking about-- we had somebody there that-- to talk us about-- about Jabotinsky, the big capo of the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't remember too much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know that the synagogue was across from-- from a-- a river, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When it was-- we had a lot of the rain, that became a river.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And across from that was a synagogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very close to-- to the house, in walking distance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't remember what it looks like right now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I attended from-- from elementary school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was about the five and four-- nine years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After I finished school, once I couldn't go to any university-- and my father arranged that I work for the same newspaper he was doing, at that time just translating from Italian to Greek or French to Greek at that time, for a while.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1938, '38 to '40.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In-- I was 16, 17.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
